\v 2 Ngi\add thi\add*: Gcina umlayo wenkosi, lanjengokwesifungo sikaNkulunkulu\x + 3.18.\x*\x + Eks. 22.11. 2 Sam. 21.7. 1 Kho. 2.43. 1 Lan. 29.24. Roma 13.5.\x*.
\v 3 Ungaphangisi\x + 7.9.\x* ukusuka phambi kwayo\x + 10.4.\x*, ungemi edabeni olubi, ngoba yenza konke ekuthandayo\x + 1 Lan. 20.4. Hlab. 1.1.\x*.
\v 4 Lapho okulelizwi lenkosi khona kulamandla\x + 8.8.\x*; njalo ngubani ongathi kuyo: Wenzani\x + Jobe 9.12. Jobe 34.18.\x*?
\v 5 Lowo ogcina umlayo kayikwazi into embi, lenhliziyo yohlakaniphileyo iyasazi isikhathi lokwahlulela\x + 12.14.\x*.
