\v 6 Ngoba kulo lonke udaba kulesikhathi\x + 3.1.\x* lokwahlulela\x + 12.14.\x*, ngoba ububi bomuntu bukhulu phezu kwakhe.
\v 7 Ngoba kakwazi ukuthi kuzakuba yini\x + Zaga 24.22.\x*, ngoba ngubani ongamtshela ukuthi kuzakuba nini\x + 6.12. 10.14. 9.12. 3.22.\x*?
\v 8 Kakulamuntu olamandla phezu komoya\x + 7.19.\x* ukubamba umoya\x + Jobe 14.5.\x*, njalo kalamandla osukwini lokufa\x + 8.8.\x*; njalo kakukho ukukhululwa kuleyompi\x + Dute. 20.5-8.\x*, lobubi kabuyikukhulula abaninibo\x + 5.11.\x*.
\v 9 Konke lokhu ngikubonile, nganikela inhliziyo yami emsebenzini wonke owenziwa ngaphansi kwelanga; kulesikhathi lapho umuntu abusa khona umuntu kube yikulimala kwakhe.
