\v 10 Ngokunjalo-ke ngabona ababi bengcwatshwa\x + Esta 4.16.\x*, ababevela njalo baye endaweni engcwele\x + Mat. 24.15. Neh. 11.1.\x*, abasebekhohlakele emzini lapho ababenze khona okunjalo. Lokhu lakho kuyize\x + 9.5. Zaga 10.7.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba isigwebo \add nge\add*senzo esibi singenziwa masinyane\x + Hlab. 10.6. 50.21. Isa. 26.10. Roma 2.4,5. 2 Pet. 3.9.\x*, ngenxa yalokho inhliziyo yabantwana babantu igcwele ngaphakathi kwabo ukwenza okubi\x + Esta 7.5. Seb. 5.3.\x*.
\v 12 Lanxa isoni sisenza okubi izikhathi ezilikhulu, le\add nsuku\x + Isa. 65.20.\x* z\add*aso zelulwe\x + 8.12. 7.15.\x*\x + Dute. 4.40. 12.25. Isa. 3.10.\x*, kube kanti sibili ngiyazi ukuthi\x + Dute. 4.40. 12.25. Isa. 3.10.\x* kuzabalungela labo abamesabayo uNkulunkulu, abesabayo phambi kwakhe\x + Hlab. 37.10,11,18,19. Zaga 1.32.33. Mat. 25.34,41.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa omubi kakuyikumlungela\x + Hlab. 37.10,11,18,19. Zaga 1.32.33. Mat. 25.34,41.\x*\x + Isa. 3.11.\x*; futhi kayikwelula insuku \add zakhe\add*; unjengesithunzi ngoba kesabi phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Jobe 14.2.\x*.
\v 14 Kukhona okuyize okwenziwayo emhlabeni, ukuthi bakhona abalungileyo abehlelwa njengokomsebenzi wababi\x + 7.15. 9.1-3. Hlab. 73.14.\x*, bakhona lababi abehlelwa njengokomsebenzi wabalungileyo. Ngathi: Lokhu lakho kuyize\x + Jobe 21.7.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho mina ngababaza intokozo; ngoba umuntu kalalutho oluhle ngaphansi kwelanga, ngaphandle kokudla lokunatha lokuthokoza\x + 2.24.\x*, ngoba lokhu kuzahlala laye ekutshikatshikeni kwakhe \add e\add*nsuk\add wini\add* zempilo yakhe uNkulunkulu amnike zona ngaphansi kwelanga\x + Gen. 29.34.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Lapho nganikela inhliziyo ukwazi inhlakanipho lokubona umsebenzi owenziwa emhlabeni, (ngoba futhi ukhona ongaboni ubuthongo ngamehlo akhe emini lebusuku\x + 5.3.\x*)
\v 17 ngasengibona wonke umsebenzi kaNkulunkulu ukuthi umuntu kalakho ukufumana umsebenzi owenziwayo ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 3.11. Jobe 5.9.\x*; ngoba lanxa umuntu etshikatshika ukukudinga, kube kanti kayikukufumana; yebo futhi, lanxa ohlakaniphileyo angathi uyazi, kayikuba lakho ukukuthola\x + Hlab. 73.16.\x*.
